{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Forms","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>아래의 페이지에서는 Web Form의 접근성을 향상시키는 여러 가지 테크닉을 소개합니다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/Basic_form_hints\" title=\"Basic form hints\">Basic form hints</a>: 무효 값 혹은 필수 필드에 힌트나 설명을 추가합니다.&nbsp;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/alerts\" title=\"alerts\">Alerts</a>: 클라이언트 측의 검증에서 발생한 에러 메시지를 표시하기 위해 alert를&nbsp;사용합니다.&nbsp;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/Multipart_labels\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/aria/forms/Multipart_labels\">Multi-part labels</a>: 각 폼 안의 컨트롤로&nbsp;복잡한 폼 레이블을 사용합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>유사한 콘텐츠를 다루고 있는&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120801225355/http://yaccessibilityblog.com/library/aria-invalid-form-inputs.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Yahoo! article on form validation and ARIA</a>&nbsp;도 봐주세요.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"아래의 페이지에서는 Web Form의 접근성을 향상시키는 여러 가지 테크닉을 소개합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Forms","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Formularios","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Formulaires","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"フォーム","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Formulários","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Forms","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Forms","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/accessibility/aria/forms","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/accessibility/aria/forms/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"접근성"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms","title":"Forms"}],"pageTitle":"Forms - 접근성 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}